call it anything - has created us

00:01:11.692 --> 00:01:20.392
and the way we have become human-beings,
one can see very clearly,

00:01:21.073 --> 00:01:34.983
there has to be some purpose. If so,
then we have to find out that purpose.

00:01:38.433 --> 00:01:48.893
