whatever we know today about ourselves

00:01:48.893 --> 00:02:04.138
and our being and our purpose, is not 
sufficient to convince us of

00:02:05.498 --> 00:02:12.217
our importance, of our glory and the
need for this force to create us.

00:02:17.227 --> 00:02:28.957
