here, why are we made human-beings

00:02:31.715 --> 00:02:39.055
- are we able to find out with this
human instrument we have got?

00:02:39.055 --> 00:02:43.928
With our human awareness can we
find out why are we here,

00:02:44.418 --> 00:02:55.698
why are we made or is there anything
else provided within us that can give us

00:03:01.243 --> 00:03:13.663
the ideas, the knowledge about ourselves.
